General.Name: Dillard's Inc
General.Description: Dillard's, Inc. operates retail department stores in the southeastern, southwestern, and midwestern areas of the United States. Its stores offer merchandise, including fashion apparel for women, men, and children; and accessories, cosmetics, home furnishings, and other consumer goods. The company also engages in the general contracting construction activities. Dillard's, Inc. was founded in 1938 and is based in Little Rock, Arkansas.
